\function nhn-deliveries() [[Leveranse]tagging[]]

Configuration for the deliveries (Leveranser) group-by tree.

* `nhn-deliveries` — all tiddlers tagged `Leveranse`.

Grouped by `nhn-year` → `nhn-month` (shared with the business-review tree); deliveries lacking a year or month tag fall into the `(Uten år)` / `(Uten måned)` buckets, sorted last.
